{"title":"CalculadoraHAND iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neurología/CalculadoraHAND iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Calculadora\\NHAND","guid":"mC_lDK0VrvmqJcHEnPAtAA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Propósito de la\\NAplicación","guid":"6hIdASfqIbAYQ3kM8O0k0g","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Herramienta web de evaluación neurocognitiva para estudio de prevalencia HAND","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Setting → Hospital Puerto Montt, Servicio Infectología","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"Población objetivo → adultos VIH+ en control","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Diseño en 2 etapas → tamizaje (MoCA) + evaluación funcional (CDR)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Clasificación automática según CRITERIOS FRASCATI (Antinori 2007)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"Optimizada para TABLET/MÓVIL (max-width 480px)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Flujo de Evaluación\\N(Wizard)","guid":"tiRvusRF14LfbNYBS5mIXg","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"PASO 1 →\\NConfiguración del\\NPaciente","guid":"ruzeZsP1-bY2GritqUaPeA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Edad (años) → determina grupo etario para Tabla 1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Escolaridad (años) → determina grupo educacional para Tabla 2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Ambos datos SON OBLIGATORIOS antes de avanzar","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"8","text":"PASO 2 →\\NEvaluación MoCA\\N(7 dominios)","guid":"Oqh26tL0Zt6uZlyXvwUuxQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"Codificación → aprendizaje de 5 palabras (ROSTRO-SEDA-IGLESIA-CLAVEL-ROJO)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"Visuoespacial/Ejecutivo\\N→ /5 puntos","guid":"wlbiX99cj4DDYzjT1zmhkQ","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Alternancia TMT-B adaptado (1 pt)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Copia del cubo (1 pt)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"Dibujo del reloj (3 pts → contorno, números, manecillas)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"Identificación\\N→ /3 puntos","guid":"4fBHRzlU37FQZ_5eWzxu7Q","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"Nombrar 3 animales (león, rinoceronte, camello)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"13","text":"Atención →\\N/6 puntos","guid":"i55OC1f5MuIvNhQxQwUtfw","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Repetición de dígitos directos (1 pt)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Repetición de dígitos inversos (1 pt)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Detección de letras/golpe en A (1 pt)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Sustracción seriada de 7 (3 pts)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"13","text":"Lenguaje →\\N/3 puntos","guid":"tNrlNCTXfXC-Pv0cv4Rerw","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Repetición de 2 frases (2 pts)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Fluidez verbal letra F ≥11 palabras (1 pt)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"13","text":"Abstracción → /2 puntos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"2 pares de semejanzas","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"13","text":"Recuerdo diferido → /5 puntos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"5 palabras aprendidas al inicio","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"13","text":"Orientación → /6 puntos","guid":"","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Fecha, mes, año, día, lugar, ciudad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"13","text":"Puntaje bruto máximo → 30 puntos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"8","text":"PASO 3 → Entrevista CDR\\N(6 dominios)","guid":"TYWNfwVvYS8GBdGOj-OlvA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"Memoria → olvidos leves a severos (0, 0.5, 1, 2, 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"Orientación → tiempo y lugar (0, 0.5, 1, 2, 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"36","text":"Juicio y resolución → manejo de problemas (0, 0.5, 1, 2, 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"36","text":"Vida social → trabajo, compras, reuniones (0, 0.5, 1, 2, 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"36","text":"Hogar y aficiones → tareas domésticas, hobbies (0, 0.5, 1, 2, 3)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"36","text":"Cuidado personal → higiene, vestimenta (0, 0.5, 1, 2, 3)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"43","parent":"8","text":"LÓGICA DE OMISIÓN\\N(SKIP LOGIC)","guid":"eYKTXvY0XYpWSijfMl27xA","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"SI CDR Vida Social = 0\\NY CDR Hogar = 0","guid":"KNrDWDt-QkwKAURVqhIH1A","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"SE ASUME independencia funcional completa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"CDR Cuidado Personal → asignado automáticamente = 0","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"44","text":"Lawton → asignado automáticamente = 8/8","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"44","text":"Barthel → asignado automáticamente = 100/100","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"44","text":"AHORRA TIEMPO en pacientes funcionalmente independientes","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"50","parent":"43","text":"SI CDR Vida Social > 0 O CDR Hogar > 0","guid":"HPPMD1JqHNU6JUak1ZuWpQ","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"Se aplican TODAS las escalas funcionales","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"8","text":"PASO 4 → Escalas Funcionales\\N(si aplica)","guid":"AE6-MG51imxDE206lC21Wg","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Lawton (AIVD)\\N→ 8 ítems,\\Npuntaje 0-8","guid":"tUD3yU-SpPm5uEjm01umWQ","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"Teléfono, compras, comida, casa, lavado, transporte, medicamentos, dinero","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Cada ítem → 1 (independiente) o 0 (dependiente)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"Barthel (ABVD) →\\N10 ítems, puntaje\\N0-100","guid":"inM27qQkltTKv2KbLe-XEg","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Comer, lavarse, vestirse, arreglarse, deposición, micción, retrete, traslado, deambular, escaleras","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"Puntajes variables por ítem (0-5, 0-10, 0-15)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"8","text":"PASO 5 → Resultado y Clasificación Frascati","guid":"","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"Integra puntaje MoCA normalizado + CDR global","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"0","text":"Conversión Normativa MoCA\\N(Gaete 2020)","guid":"4VKXErRLKaxjinqeZkch9Q","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"CONCEPTO CLAVE → puntaje bruto NO se interpreta directamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Proceso en 2 etapas secuenciales","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"TABLA 1 →\\NAjuste por\\NEdad","guid":"HIYIm5XHSsugEP1nPer4pA","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Puntaje bruto (0-30) → Puntaje Equivalente (PE) intermedio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"4 grupos etarios → <50, 50-59, 60-69, ≥70 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"A MAYOR EDAD → puntaje equivalente MÁS ALTO para mismo bruto","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"Rango resultante → PE 1-16","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"64","text":"Ejemplo → bruto 25 en <50a = PE 5 vs ≥70a = PE 11","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"61","text":"TABLA 2 →\\NAjuste por\\NEscolaridad","guid":"CKdJB6FNHzbqanZVVe29yQ","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"PE intermedio (de Tabla 1) → PE definitivo + Percentil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"2 grupos de escolaridad → 7-12 años vs >12 años","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"70","text":"MENOR ESCOLARIDAD → PE se INCREMENTA (ajuste protector)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"70","text":"Ejemplo → PE intermedio 8, escolaridad 7-12a → PE final 10 (p50)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"70","text":"Ejemplo → PE intermedio 8, escolaridad >12a → PE final 8 (p25)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"61","text":"Interpretación del PE Final\\N(Puntaje Escalar)","guid":"ZLFtzpIuEqX-dbL4dqZd0w","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"PE ≥ 8 → NORMAL (sin deterioro cognitivo)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"PE = 7 → PROBABLE DCL (deterioro cognitivo leve)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"PE 5-6 → DCM LEVE (deterioro cognitivo mayor leve)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"PE 3-4 → DCM MODERADO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"76","text":"PE 1-2 → DCM SEVERO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"61","text":"PUNTO DE CORTE para estudio HAND → PE < 8 = ALTERADO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"0","text":"Algoritmo CDR Global\\N(Washington University)","guid":"6VSjxXCt0qmnALsIwVev1A","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"Memoria es el DOMINIO PRIMARIO","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"5 dominios secundarios → orientación, juicio, vida social, hogar, cuidado personal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"83","text":"Regla principal → si ≥3 secundarios IGUALES a Memoria → CDR = Memoria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"83","text":"Si >3 secundarios MAYORES que Memoria → CDR = moda de los mayores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"83","text":"Si >3 secundarios MENORES que Memoria → CDR = moda de los menores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"83","text":"Regla especial\\NMemoria = 0.5","guid":"UjCIePjs24VgnbKNnjYflQ","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Si ≥3 secundarios ≥ 1 → CDR = 1","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Si < 3 secundarios ≥ 1 → CDR = 0.5","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"83","text":"Regla especial\\NMemoria = 0","guid":"Te946poqy6-aDc2pwrJwhw","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Si ≥3 secundarios ≥ 0.5 → CDR = 0.5","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"92","text":"Si < 3 secundarios ≥ 0.5 → CDR = 0","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"95","parent":"83","text":"En caso de empate → se usa MODA de todos los dominios","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación Frascati\\N(Antinori 2007)","guid":"bAN060rsce_wcSXgtEyaig","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Cruza 2 ejes → rendimiento cognitivo (MoCA) × impacto funcional (CDR)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"MoCA Normal (PE ≥ 8) + CDR 0 → SIN ALTERACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"No cumple criterios HAND","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"MoCA Alterado (PE < 8)\\N+ CDR 0 → ANI","guid":"lArD71zzqEoue9W4QotNUg","children":[{"id":"101","parent":"100","text":"Deterioro Neurocognitivo Asintomático","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"100","text":"Déficit cognitivo SIN repercusión funcional","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"100","text":"Categoría MÁS FRECUENTE en era TARV (~50% de HAND)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"100","text":"RIESGO 2-6× de progresar a deterioro sintomático (CHARTER)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"96","text":"MoCA Alterado (PE < 8)\\N+ CDR 0.5 → MND","guid":"qLyl8It3kn_7EZDPrLQg3Q","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"Trastorno Neurocognitivo Leve asociado a VIH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"Déficit cognitivo CON impacto LEVE en AVD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"Interfiere con actividades instrumentales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"109","parent":"96","text":"MoCA Alterado (PE < 8)\\N+ CDR ≥ 1 → HAD","guid":"NLMTYwgqCLETqfaZlbVYsw","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"Demencia Asociada al VIH","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"Déficit cognitivo CON impacto MARCADO en AVD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"109","text":"Prevalencia reducida en era TARV (~2-5%)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"113","parent":"96","text":"Requisito diagnóstico adicional\\N→ excluir causas confundentes","guid":"7JYYfOc0GN71qbf-nryqSQ","children":[{"id":"114","parent":"113","text":"Infecciones oportunistas del SNC","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"113","text":"Abuso de sustancias/alcohol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"113","text":"Trastornos psiquiátricos graves","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"113","text":"Lesión cerebral previa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"113","text":"Delirium activo","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"0","text":"Arquitectura\\NTécnica","guid":"xYSn96tz8rKXHYePj2RHWw","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Stack → React 18.2.0 + Babel standalone (JSX en navegador)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"React vía CDN → react.production.min.js + react-dom.production.min.js","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"Archivo único HTML → ~2500 líneas, autocontenido","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"Interfaz wizard → navegación paso a paso con barra de progreso","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"Modo oscuro → toggle automático con CSS variables","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"119","text":"Responsive → optimizado para tablets y móviles (max-width 480px)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"119","text":"Despliegue → Netlify Drop (drag & drop), o compartir archivo directo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"127","parent":"0","text":"Ventajas para\\Nel Evaluador","guid":"9c4V58xkV5m-F6xIVu6dpQ","children":[{"id":"128","parent":"127","text":"Elimina cálculo manual de normas (2 tablas complejas)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"127","text":"Reduce errores de conversión normativa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"127","text":"Algoritmo CDR automático (reglas complejas de Washington)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"131","parent":"127","text":"Skip logic ahorra 5-10 min en pacientes independientes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"127","text":"Scripts guía → instrucciones textuales para cada dominio MoCA y CDR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"127","text":"Resultado inmediato con clasificación Frascati integrada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"127","text":"No requiere conexión a internet","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"1. Antinori A et al. Updated research nosology for HIV-associated neurocognitive disorders. Neurology. 2007;69(18):1789-99.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"2. Nasreddine ZS et al. The Montreal Cognitive Assessment, MoCA: a brief screening tool for mild cognitive impairment. J Am Geriatr Soc. 2005;53(4):695-9.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"3. Gaete M et al. Datos normativos del MoCA en población chilena. Rev Med Chile. 2020;148:1-10.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"4. Morris JC. The Clinical Dementia Rating (CDR): current version and scoring rules. Neurology. 1993;43(11):2412-4.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"135","text":"5. Hughes CP et al. A new clinical scale for the staging of dementia. Br J Psychiatry. 1982;140:566-72.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"135","text":"6. Heaton RK et al. HIV-associated neurocognitive disorders persist in the era of potent antiretroviral therapy: CHARTER Study. Neurology. 2010;75(23):2087-96.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"135","text":"7. Ku NS et al. HIV-associated neurocognitive disorder in HIV-infected Koreans. HIV Med. 2014;15(8):470-7.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"135","text":"8. Carvallo C, Ramos-Henderson M. Trail making test B&W: Normative study for Chilean population. J Neuropsychol. 2024;18(3):415-26.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"135","text":"9. Lawton MP, Brody EM. Assessment of older people: self-maintaining and instrumental activities of daily living. Gerontologist. 1969;9(3):179-86.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"135","text":"10. Mahoney FI, Barthel DW. Functional evaluation: the Barthel Index. Md State Med J. 1965;14:61-5.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":145,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Neurología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"CalculadoraHAND iPad","id":"map_1389","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"CalculadoraHAND iPad"}